# Requirements — ITAI 2376 Module 09 Lab

## System Requirements
- Python 3.8 or higher
- Google Colab (recommended) or Jupyter Notebook

---

## Python Libraries
The following libraries are required:

- gymnasium
- numpy
- matplotlib

---

## Installation Instructions
Run the following command before executing the notebook:
pip install gymnasium numpy matplotlib

---

## Hardware Requirements
- No GPU required
- CPU is sufficient
- Runs within 1–2 minutes on standard hardware or Google Colab free tier

---

## Notes
- No external datasets are required
- All training data is generated in real time using the CartPole-v1 environment
- Internet access is only needed to install dependencies
